name: BananaCoin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Bananacoin is a DAO community developed memecoin.
What makes your project unique?
The project is unique in its community-oriented approach and future plans for NFTs.
History of your project.
Bananacoin is the DAO community

What’s next for your project?
The next step for the project is to expand its community and further develop its ecosystem.
What can your token be used for?
The token can be used for various purposes within the community, to vote on proposals and to participate in community activities. Also, it may have additional functionality and utility in the future as the project develops.
